ult behavior of \"add/save\" -- what files should go to annex. I see a few possible schemes we could easily set:\n- **all** -- that is what we have ATM. no .gitattributes generated, everything goes to annex unless explicitly aid to go to git\n- **largenontext** -- which would generate .gitattributes\n\n``` shell\n* annex.largefiles=(largerthan=100kb and not (mimetype=text/*))\n```\n- **nontext** -- I think this is what should be our default, and which would generate .gitattributes\n\n``` shell\n* annex.largefiles=not (mimetype=text/*)\n```\n\nI haven't tried those specific values for largefiles yet, but according to https://git-annex.branchable.com/tips/largefiles/  should work, right @joeyh ?\n\npossibly relates to #925 (create-sibling), #996 (`add --to=git|annex`) ...\n", "closed_by": {"login": "mih", "id": 136479, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEzNjQ3OQ==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/136479?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih", "html_url": "https://github.com/mih", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/1021/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/1021/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null}